OL,3,CLearner driver arrested for drug
OL,4,Cdriving in middle of test
OL,6,FA learner motorist has been arrested
OL,7,Ffor drug driving in the middle of his
OL,8,Fdriving test.
OL,10,FOfficers on patrol stopped a vehicle
OL,11,Fin King Street, St Helens, at about
OL,12,F5pm on Sunday 1 March after spotting a
OL,13,Fbrake light was not working.
OL,15,FA smell of cannabis was noticeable
OL,16,Fwhen they spoke to the driver who
OL,17,Fsubsequently failed a drugs wipe test
OL,18,Fand was also found to be in possession
OL,19,Fof cannabis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
