OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772568684
OL,3,CLearner driver arrested for drug
OL,4,Cdriving in middle of test
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man from Wigan, Greater
OL,7,FManchester, was arrested on suspicion
OL,8,Fof drug driving and taken into police
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FHe has since been released under
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FRoads Policing Inspector Simon Wilson
OL,15,Fsaid: "Although some people may find
OL,16,Fthe humour in the fact someone on a
OL,17,Fdriving test was arrested, drug
OL,18,Fdriving is no laughing matter.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
