CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772568684
OL,3,CLearner driver arrested for drug
OL,4,Cdriving in middle of test
OL,6,F"It is incredibly dangerous and
OL,7,Fselfish to get behind the wheel of a
OL,8,Fvehicle under the influence of drugs
OL,9,Fand it's an offence we take seriously
OL,10,Fat Merseyside Police.
OL,12,F"Our stance on illegal substances is
OL,13,Fclear. Nobody should be taking them.
OL,15,F"But even if you choose to break the
OL,16,Flaw and take illegal drugs, that does
OL,17,Fnot give you the right to endanger the
OL,18,Flives of innocent people on the roads
OL,19,Fwho have no way of knowing you are
OL,20,Fdriving intoxicated."
